{"tid":2504622,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"秘魯前總統偷打中國疫苗半年還拼選戰 與妻雙確診","createTime":"2021-04-26T04:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T11:32:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4934b9c7aed999796505d4fae592762faddb4247","tid":2504622,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:19:08.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎禍害全球，北京當局趁機展開疫苗外交，只是，又被打臉了！秘魯前總統畢<br />\n斯卡拉（Martin Vizcarra）去年就接種中國疫苗，他25日在推特宣布，雖然已經採取避<br />\n免將病毒帶回家　的措施，他與妻子仍然雙雙確診，目前正在隔離中；而本月他才參加大<br />\n型造勢活動，雖然他上台時全程戴著口罩，但身邊圍繞大批支持者，無法保持社交距離，<br />\n仍引起疑慮。<br />\n <br />\n畢斯卡拉在2018~2020年間擔任秘魯總統，卸任後轉戰國會，最近贏得選舉。不過現年58<br />\n歲的他在今年2月爆出利用職權，在秘魯啟動全國疫苗接種計畫前，就秘密在去年10月提<br />\n早接種中國國藥疫苗的醜聞，國會暫時禁止他不能從事國會議員一職。<br />\n <br />\n這位前總統畢斯卡拉否認接種醜聞，辯稱他與妻子、兄弟是參加臨床試驗。據了解，該醜<br />\n聞牽連達470人，害秘魯衛生部長、外交部長等人下台。<br />\n <br />\n好吧！不管是接種偷跑還是人體試驗，畢斯卡拉去年10月接種中國疫苗至今半年，與妻子<br />\n正式雙雙確診。讓民眾害怕的是，畢斯卡拉投入國會議員選戰，一直到本月中旬投票前，<br />\n身邊一直都有大批支持者圍繞，現在只能祈盼大家有確實戴好口罩，做好防疫，因為顯然<br />\n打了中國疫苗，也不保證安全。<br />\n <br />\n根據美國約翰霍普金斯大學台灣時間26日上午9時統計，人口3300多萬的秘魯，目前確診<br />\n人數高達175萬人，已經有5萬9400多人死亡，嚴重程度排在全球前20名內，疫情相當嚴峻<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-26/568687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-04-26%2F568687&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepLccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=7dc5fee3\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-04-26/568687</a>"},{"pid":"7cdbf455f54d43be4552c96fc2379146ca1537d6","tid":2504622,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"爭住食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d12457812c9ba62d144510eb90d7380214f7162","tid":2504622,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"去年接種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f089b4dcea21a0fbbd7fba56788d778d5a983b","tid":2504622,"uid":327462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"支國疫苗都要偷打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041e4a9ce6e4f28176f625ad96130dddf9012e01","tid":2504622,"uid":228955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:43:17.000Z","msg":"China virus"},{"pid":"a9971991d0510b28b166ad6ef575976d8c4e7b39","tid":2504622,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cdbf455f54d43be4552c96fc2379146ca1537d6","tid":2504622,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"爭住食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">以為自己食屎食著豆，博大霧打先。點知一樣仆街</span>"},{"pid":"b021e6056d000659e541a193da842ced1476f85d","tid":2504622,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"乜都唔打咪冇事囉"},{"pid":"a0d850cb3be55bf1bf55874d6a1bfc1581fcab62","tid":2504622,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7746fc40564a75d0dd95da96ff2814d8545e4834","tid":2504622,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9971991d0510b28b166ad6ef575976d8c4e7b39","tid":2504622,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cdbf455f54d43be4552c96fc2379146ca1537d6","tid":2504622,"uid":185656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"爭住食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">以為自己食屎食著豆，博大霧打先。點知一樣仆街</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"食豆食著屎就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class